item.description: Hey everyone come on up to Rumney. Yes it's a Monday but what better reason to take a day off! Less crowds and a "guest" climber from AZ, Joe (who organizes for AZ climbing meetup) will be here for some NH climbing! Check the message board for contact with Joe! Climbing is sport climbing and top roping, so all level climbing is welcome. Let me know if you need to know how to get there.
item.name: Rumney Rendezvbous!!
